Reasoning: The paper deals with the capacity of a communication channel in the context of stabilizing a linear system, which involves concepts from information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also introduces the concept of an anytime rate-region, which is a generalization of the concept of capacity, and discusses its properties, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the paper provides an example involving a binary erasure channel, which could fall under the category of mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
